reviewText: A great CD for tango lovers!  The dancing is wonderful although pure tango/milonga dancing would have been great to see with these dancers.

The video shows the unique dance, Argentina Tango.  The Argentina Tango is quite different from regular Tango.  The video takes your on a tour of the different Tango spots in Buenos Aires.  The performers are spectacular.
Thought it was the HDNet 1 hour documentary on Tango. Same title, same producer, same title. They got me! This product was of very poor quality, not the HD production I had hoped for.
